						<div class="fusion-sep-clear"></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-single sep-solid" style="border-color:#e0dede;border-top-width:1px;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;"></div><div class="fusion-text"><h3 style="text-align: center;">Beautifully located in the historic 1810 House of Warwick, NY, Bertolini &amp; Co., offers a full-range of interior decorating and design services for a timeless home and garden, including window treatments, upholstery, wall and floor coverings and of course, antique treasures galore.</h3>
</div><div class="fusion-sep-clear"></div><div class="fusion-separator fusion-full-width-sep sep-single sep-solid" style="border-color:#e0dede;border-top-width:1px;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;margin-top:;"></div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>

