						<div class="fusion-text"><h3 class="title">About Us</h3>
<figure class="wp-block-image"></figure>
</div><div class="fusion-text"><p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-2428" src="https://www.bertolinico.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Chessie-e1578162396811.jpg" alt="" width="400" height="404" /></p>
</div><div class="fusion-text"><p>2011 marked the opening of our new interior design shop and antiques emporium, Bertolini &amp; Co. located in the heart of historic Warwick, NY, on Main St. on Lewis Park.  Michael Bertolini heads the design and management team specializing in unique and hard-to–find 18th and 19th century antiques and full service interior design and garden design.  Chessie here? Well, she sleeps, I mean, guards the shop.</p>
